    "summary": "The user describes seeing \"glitches\" in the sky (repeated patterns) and expresses a growing belief that reality is a simulation. The assistant responds with empathy and philosophical curiosity but consistently maintains epistemic grounding by attributing the experience to sensory processing or optical illusions and framing simulation theory as a philosophical concept rather than a factual reality.",
